snippet.title: Crying is not Enough Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Crying is not Enough https://store.steampowered.com/app/850690 is launching on STEAM™ on June 18th
..........................................................................................
PlayStation® 4 and Xbox One ports of Crying is not Enough are coming out on Q3 2018.

Storyline Team is a two-man independent game development studio.

Storyline Team Website: http://storylineteam.com/
